Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.19,0:00:07.93,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片轻描淡写地讲述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.34,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要过度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.77,0:00:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  这是土特产
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.22,0:00:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煎饼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  总是布丁怕你们会腻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上给你上茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盐提了一点点味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一点点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.48,0:00:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一点点勇气的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能把这个交给丽子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生都喜欢爱情片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到去电影院约会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是必选甜蜜的爱情片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.41,0:00:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说喜欢爱情片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是随便和谁都能看的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.74,0:01:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说一起看的同伴比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在昏暗的影院中挨着坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互依偎在一块
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去度过甜蜜的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶要凉了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.38,0:01:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.17,0:01:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,销量突破1000万本的国民漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待已久的电影化！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经发誓不再恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.37,0:01:52.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}火热上映中！！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个秋天  最催泪的恋爱故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,310)}现在、开始恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香好像喜欢看电影哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  说到高中生健康地约会内容就是电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以和女儿们一起享受电影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  南春香喜欢什么样的电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过约会的话  爱情片不是板上钉钉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  爱情片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时这部爱情片似乎相当催泪哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,催泪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么甜怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆米花不应该是咸的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是邪门歪道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影院里焦糖味才是王道  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼你这是只喜欢甜食的小鬼的味觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的泪水由我来擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要为我拭去汗水就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树  喜欢电影什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是别人送的  方便的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影票啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想作为之前烤肉的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐邀我去看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么样的电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美相当喜欢看电影对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看恋爱进行时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个什么样的电影来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  听说是相当催泪的爱情片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.74,0:05:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗  是催泪的爱情片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张票…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是接连不断命运的巧合下两人坠入爱河的电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样的可喜欢这类电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对这种电影没兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我周围的人都这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我再去问问别人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树的那个眼神是非常悲伤的眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么悲伤的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是什么悲伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢电影吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.86,0:06:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  算是…比较喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.52,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  被邀请去看电影了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被…被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被谁邀请不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超认真的爱情片哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是相当让人笑不出来的恋爱故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方的确认真过头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两张票叠在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊那家伙真是个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请别人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该给别人一张自己留一张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这并不是被邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让她去邀请别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出了相当悲伤的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤的眼神？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方也是从中意的女生那里拿到了这电影票吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.77,0:07:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个煎饼  带一点点咸味非常好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  那个票子春香姐姐不是也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶  带一点点咸味真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tabasco
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Spicyman
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  还没有去邀请吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请给我票子的人去看电影算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是为什么把票子给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人心什么的不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那么来问男孩子这个问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问健
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是作罢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你们二人认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.53,0:08:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在拐角转弯的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在买饮料的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是接连不断命运的巧合下两人坠入爱河的模式啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在抱歉  我对比我小的没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没有那个打算！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  用不着问藤冈的男人心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.63,0:09:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于偶然原因这里有两张电影票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只能由你们两个去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动惊人地同步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别模仿我啊  羞死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是我要说的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  冷静些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来喝杯茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步成这样真是佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给这种现象取名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BINGO的话怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一般
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么合拍怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:57.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8次合拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刷新最高纪录了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:09:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你够了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.21,0:10:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的厕所只有一个所以请按顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.82,0:10:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  用猜拳决定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会出现吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:13.48,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:18.06,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步率真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.16,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会更新纪录吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头～布！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经数不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉尼斯纪录了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样永远也决定不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.87,0:10:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强你先去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忍得住么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比忍耐力我可不会输啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公共厕所的话附近是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我的双脚可以以马赫的速度奔去那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是超马赫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
